high_descs: Turn right, move to the sink.
Pick up the gray plate on the counter, right of the sink.
Turn around, bring the plate back to the fridge on your left.
Chill the plate in the fridge.
Bring the chilled plate to the left, to the cabinet under the sink.
Put the chilled plate in the left cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate in the left cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the counter  beside the sink
Pick up the plate on the counter
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the plate then close the fridge
Turn left and head to the left side cabinet below the sink
Open the cabinet and put in the plate then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled plate in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn right and head to the sink
Pick up the baking pan from the counter on the right
Turn around and go to towards the wall then turn left at the fridge
Put the baking pan on a shelf in the fridge and wait a bit, then take the pan out of the fridge
Turn around and then turn right and head towards the sink
Put the baking pan in the cupboard under the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled baking pan in the cupboard under the sink
